<paragraph blockId="1.[136,1452,236,468]" pageId="1" pageNumber="317">
Etymology. The species is named in honour of Prof. Hengwen Luo for providing the 
<typeStatus box="[1077,1123,306,330]" pageId="1" pageNumber="317">type</typeStatus>
specimens and the information on the biology and immature stages of this new species.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[136,1452,236,468]" pageId="1" pageNumber="317">
Remarks. The new species is the second known species in this genus. The 
<typeStatus box="[1002,1048,376,400]" pageId="1" pageNumber="317">type</typeStatus>
